        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3461392037" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10659402486763181915">Lovely, insightful, and biting writing, with a few parts that felt manipulatively cruel (the one that got to me was an absolutely unnecessary killing of a young boy). Morrison was an incredible talent and is much missed.</span>

          </span>
